mobile/odn-20171203-1203_00176_033.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年12月05日<br />\n近期澳門海關連環爆出管理不善醜聞，惟當局仍懶理批評，遭外界炮轟官僚、水平低，「衰過清朝」，事發多時對事件都全無交代。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171205/mobile/odn-20171205-1205_00176_050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171205%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20171205-1205_00176_050.html&d=6zjhOazpj6N4jXPNlI5NiZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=408095d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171205/mobile/odn-20171205-1205_00176_050.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年12月07日<br />\n澳門政府管治亂象叢生，衰過清朝。單是設計費用便達逾兩億元公帑的離島醫院一拖六年，至今仍未有圖則，完工遙遙無期。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171207/mobile/odn-20171207-1207_00176_010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171207%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20171207-1207_00176_010.html&d=6zjhOazpj6N4jXPNlI5NiZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b496215a\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171207/mobile/odn-20171207-1207_00176_010.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年12月08日<br />\n管治亂象 衰過清朝 澳門勢爆出「歐文龍第二」<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171208/mobile/odn-20171208-1208_00176_040.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171208%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20171208-1208_00176_040.html&d=6zjhOazpj6N4jXPNlI5NiZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8faf0e64\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171208/mobile/odn-20171208-1208_00176_040.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年12月10日<br />\n筆下風雲：衰過清朝豈無因<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171210/mobile/odn-20171210-1210_00184_005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171210%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20171210-1210_00184_005.html&d=6zjhOazpj6N4jXPNlI5NiZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=bd90564b\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171210/mobile/odn-20171210-1210_00184_005.html</a>"}